<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:43%;"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment:5000contestfourminorsix-5/koi"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/fragment:5000contestfourminorsix-5/koi/medium.jpg" style="width:43%;" alt="koi" class="image" /></a>
